<p><strong>Show notes for TMO To Go: Mac Geek Gab For the week of July 18th, 2005</strong></p>
<p>Podcast Link: <a href="http://mp3.macobserver.com/podcast/mgg7.mp3" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">TMO To Go: Mac Geek Gab, July 18th, 2005</a></p>
<p>Back from Macworld, Dave finds lightning struck his home and office network and talks about what to do to make sure this never happens to you. That leads to quite a few tangents where John and Dave explore various topics, including their overall take on Macworld Expo Boston 2005.</p>
